{defaultcss}

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">

<div id="ebay-description" class="nojs">
		<div class="container">
				<img class="logo" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0624/1527/4181/files/Element_9LogoBLACK.png?v=1663068944" />
		</div>
		<div class="container">
				<div class="block">
						<div class="row">
								<div class="span12">
										<h2>{Title}</h2>
								</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
								<div class="span12">
										<!--startcodistodescription - DO NOT REMOVE-->
										{include field="EbayDescription"}
										<!--endcodistodescription - DO NOT REMOVE-->
								</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
								<div class="span12 text-center">
										<a href="#img1">
										  <img class="logo" src="{CDNUrl}/productimages/{ProductID}.png?width=547&amp;etag={etag}">
										</a>
										<a href="#_" class="lightbox" id="img1">
											<div class="close-img">&times</div>
											<img src="{CDNUrl}/productimages/{ProductID}.png?width=800&amp;etag={etag}" />
										</a>

										{for images}
											<a href="#_" class="lightbox" id="img{position+1}">
												<div class="close-img">&times</div>
												<img src="{cdnurl}{images.src}&width=800&amp;height=600&amp;nostretch">
											</a>
										{/for}

										<div class="clearfix"></div>
										{if count(images) > 1}<hr/>{/if}
										{for images step=4}
												<div class="row image-row text-center">
														{for Images count=4 start={position}}
														<div class="span2"><a class="image fancybox" href="#img{position+1}"><img src="{cdnurl}{images.src}&width=200&amp;height=200"/></a></div>
														{/for}
												</div>
										{/for}
										<br />
								</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
								<div class="span5 buy-now">
								{if !MultiVariant}
										<a href="http://offer.{EbaySiteURL}/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?BinConfirm&amp;quantity=1&amp;fb=1&amp;item={EbayItemID}" target="_blank" class="btn btn-large btn-primary"><i class="icon-shopping-cart icon-white"></i> Acquista ora e risparmia!</a>
								{/if}
								</div>
								<div class="span7 buttons">
										<a href="http://contact.{EbaySiteURL}/ws1/eBayISAPI.dll?ShowEmailAuctionToFriend&amp;rt=nc&amp;item={EbayItemID}" target="_blank" class="btn btn"><i class="icon-bullhorn"></i> Condividi</a>
										{if EbayStoreURL}
										<a href="{EbayStoreURL}" target="_blank" class="btn btn"><i class="icon-gift"></i> Visita il nostro negozio</a>
										{/if}
										<a href="http://cgi1.{EbaySiteURL}/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?MakeTrack&amp;item={EbayItemID}" target="_blank" class="btn btn"><i class="icon-eye-open"></i> Osservare</a>
								</div>
						</div>
				</div>
		</div>
		{if SuggestedProducts}
				<div class="container">
					<div class="block" id="you_like">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="span12">
								<h2>Potrebbero piacerti anche questi prodotti</h2>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
							{for SuggestedProducts}
								<div class="span3">
									<div class="imagecenter">
										<a target="_blank" href="http://cgi.{EbaySiteURL}/{EbayItemID}"><img src="{CDNUrl}/productimages/{ID}.jpg?width=170&height=170" /></a>
									</div>
									<h4><a target="_blank" href="http://cgi.{EbaySiteURL}/{EbayItemID}">{Name}</a></h4>
								</div>
							{/for}
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
		{/if}
		<div class="container">
		<div class="tabs">

			<div class="tab">
				<input type="radio" id="tab-1" name="tab-group-1" checked>
				<label for="tab-1" style="margin-left: 2px;">Contatto</label>

				<div class="content">
					<div class="row">
						 <div class="span6">
							 <p>Per contattarci, cliccate sul pulsante sottostante. Saremo felici di aiutarvi!</p>
							 <p><a target="_blank" href="http://contact.{EbaySiteURL}/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?FindAnswers&amp;requested={EbayUserID}&amp;iid={EbayItemID}" class="btn btn-info btn-large"><i class="icon-info-sign icon-white"></i> Contatto</a></p>
						 </div>
						 <div class="span6">
							 {if MerchantName != "<to be set>"}<p>&copy; {MerchantName}</p>{/if}
						 </div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="tab">
				<input type="radio" id="tab-2" name="tab-group-1">
				<label for="tab-2">Spedizione</label>

				<div class="content">
					 <p>
              <p>Tutti i nostri prodotti vengono spediti dalla Germania.</p>
              <p>La spedizione nazionale &egrave; gratuita, mentre per i pacchi pi&ugrave; grandi ci riserviamo il diritto di addebitare un costo. Questo sar&agrave; ovviamente mostrato prima dell'acquisto.</p>
              <p>Offriamo anche spedizioni internazionali. Il costo &egrave; di 9,99&euro; - 14,99&euro;</p>
              <p>Se avete altre domande sulla spedizione o sulla vostra spedizione in particolare, non esitate a contattarci.</p>
              <p><a target="_blank" href="http://contact.{EbaySiteURL}/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?FindAnswers&amp;requested={EbayUserID}&amp;iid={EbayItemID}" class="btn btn-info btn-large"><i class="icon-info-sign icon-white"></i> Contatto</a></p>
					 </p>
				 </div>
			</div>
			<div class="tab">
			  <input type="radio" id="tab-5" name="tab-group-1">
			  <label for="tab-5">Restituzioni</label>

			  <div class="content">
          <p>La restituzione &egrave; possibile entro 30 giorni dall'acquisto.</p>
          <p>I costi della spedizione di ritorno sono a carico dell'acquirente.</p>

          <br />
						<div>{EbayReturnPolicyDescription}</div>
			   </div>
		   </div>

		</div>
		</div>

		<div class="container" id="footer">
				<!--
				The following logo and attribution needs to remain with the appropriate link back to codisto as per our terms of service
				-->
				<div class="pull-right logo">
						<span class="muted"> eBay integration</span> by
						<img class="baseline" src="{CDNUrl}/images/codisto-connect.png?width=200&amp;nostretch&amp;v=1" />
				</div>
				<img class="logo" src="{CDNUrl}/images/logo.png?width=201&nostretch&etag={LogoEtag}" />
		</div>
</div>
